      "title": "Rs. 550 Mn worth heroin seized; Mother, Son duo arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A mother and a son duo have been arrested by the Embilipitiya Police for possessing 38 Kg of heroin worth over Rs.550 Kg.",
        "The Police say that the stock of heroin was hidden in a house in Embilipitiya which was obtained on a rental basis.",
        "Police Spokesman SSP Nihal Talduwa said that a 46-year-old mother and her 22-year-old son have been arrested and further investigations are being conducted."
      ],
